Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Imbecis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por causa de vocês ele escapou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele era nossa galinha dos ovos dourados.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, seus idiotas! Vamos prender todos\Nvocês que estão atrapalhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:39.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo, Marinha?!\NNão atrapalhem o Rei do Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:41.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que está havendo aí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O pânico é geral!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Marinha veio prender o Rei do Soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e está sendo impedida pelos fãs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:50.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E de alguma forma, ele conseguiu fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maldito traidor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, notícias urgentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O músico Brook é pirata e companheiro\Nde Luffy do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado! Chegou em bora hora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A irmã Shakky pediu pra ajudar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus companheiros estão te\Nesperando no Mangue #42!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:19.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há quanto tempo! Meu coração já\Nestá batendo de ansiedade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:23.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se bem que eu não tenho coração...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Marinha entrou em ação,\Ne o Luffy está na ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:38.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos levar o Sunny até\No Mangue #42! Encontrem a gente lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:40.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que ele queria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não ouviu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:50.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Marinha. Vindo. Nós. Correr. Navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Por que está falando dessa maneira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Forme uma sentença!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei que um brutamontes feito você\Nnão entendesse orações complexas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:05.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem. Você. Depois. Fatiado.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá, tá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aliás, ouviu aquele bafafá?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.63,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É verdade. Barulho. Ali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Silêncio, seus canalhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:33.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já achamos um dos criminosos\Nque me insultaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É ele!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.09,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Primeiro, eu vou ensinar uma lição a ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:44.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou mostrar o quanto sou temível!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E quero que isto que vou fazer com ele
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sirva de aviso para vocês, meus homens!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:54.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se tentarem me sacanear,\Né assim que vão acabar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me fiz entender?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:02.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um homem com recompensa de 400 milhões\Né mesmo de dar medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é a dele?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro, Sanji, conhecem ele?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.12,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabe, é que...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já chega, seus piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:17.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy do Chapéu de Palha e seguidores!\NRendam-se sem resistir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Marinha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:23.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos bloqueando todas\Nas saídas do Mangue #46!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não vão conseguir fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?! Como é que a Marinha me descobriu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você disse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão, estamos cercados pela Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiota! Não entre em pânico!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É pra isso que recrutamos\Nos novos membros!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temos homens com recompensas\Nde mais de 100 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas são muitos...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiota! Olha só!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Use aquele soldado da Marinha\Ncomo refém para abrir caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Soldado da Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:54.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles pegaram nosso espião!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga, maldição!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.02,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está fazendo, Caribou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.49,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos usá-lo para fugir daqui!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:02.08,0:06:06.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vai dar, Grande Líder!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.62,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:13.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque este soldado aqui mentiu pra mim,\Nquando disse que não chamou a Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:28.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele imbecil ignorou ordens do capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, ele aprontou mais uma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:37.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles acham que podem mentir à vontade\Npara nós porque somos os vilões,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas isso precisa mudar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês parecem não ter nenhuma\Nintenção de se renderem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Derrotem esses piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:53.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiotas! Nosso chefe é um homem\Nde 400 milhões, Luffy do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não, Capitão! Vamos fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiotas, me escutem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Por que eles estão\Nme chamando de líder?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tenham medo! Avancem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:30.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É Lip Service Doughty, um criminoso\Ncom 88 milhões de recompensa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gostei do seu jeito de lutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tenham medo!\NPreparem-se para atirar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é o homem de 92 milhões...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Albion, o Retalhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não recuem! Lutem pela justiça!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:08:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sangue de gente hipócrita fede!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:03.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um criminoso de 210 milhões,\NCaribou do Cabelo Molhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Renda-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Você usa uma Akuma no Mi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:16.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faz bem se esforçar demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.26,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha espada...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! O que foi isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pacifistas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que as armas humanas\Nda Marinha fazem aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São os homens-kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas a Hancock falou pra eu\Nnão me meter em encrenca...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:47.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De novo, do que você\Nestá falando, afinal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pirata Luffy do Chapéu de Palha. Confirmado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:09:00.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São Pacifistas de verdade?\NEstão mirando em mim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pacifistas, é? Agora ficou interessante!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:16.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lip Service Doughty, de recompensa\Nde 88 milhões. Silenciado.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão Doughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:24.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sigam os Pacifistas! Peguem os piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:24.96,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um golpe só?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:29.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele valia 88 milhões e não foi páreo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa, não! Ei, Capitão,\Naonde o senhor vai?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esperem por mim!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.42,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiotas! Não vou enfrentar esses\Ncaras que mataram o Foughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Líder Chapéu de Palha, faça alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desse jeito, aquelas armas\Nhumanas vão matar todos nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Grande Líder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Grande Líder se foi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Grande Líder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É assim que eles chamam\No Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esperem! Minha barriga tá doendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corra, seu idiota, ou vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Imbecil! Saia do meu caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele é...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Grande Líder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que estão te\Nchamando de Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:31.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você! Não sabe quem eu sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saia do meu caminho ou vou\Nmatá-lo e arrancar suas vísceras!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:41.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você pode não saber, mas sou\Nfilho do Revolucionário Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E neto do grande herói Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:47.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu fiz meu nome na Guerra dos Maiorais!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:48.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um pirata famoso com\Nrecompensa de 400 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:55.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Chapéu de Palha não é\Num verme feito você!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que?...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:10:59.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:00.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:07.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Líder Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos eles foram tapeados\Npelo Chapéu de Palha impostor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,PX-5, quem é ele de verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Demaro Black das Três Línguas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recompensa de 26 milhões.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,26 milhões?! Então ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um impostor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles descobriram! Vamos fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que história é essa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:43.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele se fez passar pelo\NLuffy do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aproveitou que o verdadeiro está morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Eu quase fui enganado\Npor um desgraçado
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,com uma recompensazinha\Nde 26 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele estava se passando por mim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqueles Sanji e Zoro também eram falsos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:00.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São iguaizinhos aos verdadeiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Melhor dar o fora daqui\Nantes que seja tarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:09.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem enganou vocês é um idiota,\Nmas vocês são uns azarados!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vão todos vir conosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:18.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas, por coincidência, o verdadeiro\NChapéu de Palha também está por aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:23.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando ele entrou na área, PX-5 o detectou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atire nele, PX-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que história é essa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa mochila tá com toda a minha comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:51.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A-Aqui está o cartaz dele...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É ele mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então aquele cara era\No verdadeiro Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:08.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós queremos mesmo é o verdadeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:13.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é você! Vai tentar\Nme impedir de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:17.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não posso arrumar briga!\NQuero partir daqui em paz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!\NVocê não vai nem içar velas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:25.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A situação mudou de dois anos pra cá.\NAgora eu sou oficial da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E vou te capturar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,PX-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que Lento!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gia Sekando!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jetto Pisutoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:22.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Chapéu de Palha... está usando Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele derrotou o Pacifista com um só golpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Falou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que vamos nos ver de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não o deixem fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Sabia que era você!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:56.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você vive\Narrumando encrenca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:03.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora são vocês mesmos!\NHá quanto tempo, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:07.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa! Perna Negra!\NEntão eles estavam vivos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,PX-7!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fora do meu caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu o cortei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, eu quebrei o pescoço dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:33.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha! Os verdadeiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:36.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não têm nada a ver com os farsantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy, você foi o nono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca! Corta essa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anda, Luffy! Tá todo mundo\Nesperando no navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:55.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem os Chapéus de Palha fugirem!\NPeguem-nos, custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:16:00.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há quanto tempo, hein?\NComo será que está o pessoal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que felicidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, o Rei das Trevas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:33.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só vim ver como você estava,\Nmas parece que está tudo resolvido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está claramente mais forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:41.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora volte para os seus companheiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:47.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá! Rayleigh, obrigado por\Ntudo nestes dois anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:51.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não precisa ser tão formal! Ande logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:01.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou conseguir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:15.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu serei o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capturem o Chapéu de Palha imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anda, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, obrigado por tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Rayleigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por tudo mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:50.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles foram por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atrás deles! Eles não podem fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chegue ao topo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha estão\Na caminho do Mangue #42!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não os deixem fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, o Rei das Trevas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um novo começo para o meu pupilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Peguem leve com ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Que linha é essa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu recomendo que não a atravessem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:58.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ih, uma porção de Sabao-Bolsas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tem elas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Elas estão cheias de comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:05.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aposto que um certo alguém também\Ntreinou o estômago nos últimos dois anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te deixo encher o bucho depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?! Mal posso esperar\Npra comer sua comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá estão eles! Eles foram por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Eles deram a volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:19.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não temos escolha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ataquem com tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero virar uma pulga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero virar um ácaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu... Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero virar um piolho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é coisa da...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:55.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia que eram vocês\Nque estavam aprontando!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não acredito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:03.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês ainda não chegaram a lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:06.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Te conheço de Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:12.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você ainda faz aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:15.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não fala assim comigo!\NFui que te trouxe pra cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se não fosse por mim, você...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Coloque-se no seu lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma mulher de verdade!\NUma mulher de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Claro que sou! Que doença você tem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enfim, saiam logo deste lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vi navios da Marinha por aí.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Logo, eles cercarão a ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:44.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa voz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:49.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Nami! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:52.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fraaanky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Não acredito que você\Nvai abandonar o estrelato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mandou bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:07.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há quanto tempo, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês duas estão ainda mais lindas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:14.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dois anos se passaram...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, vai tocar uma pra gente?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:28.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Posso ver sua calcinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você acha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:32.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dois anos atrás, eu também não deixava!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:36.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Estou tão emocionado de revê-la...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:38.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O meu peito chega a tremer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo não tendo peito...
Dialogue: 50,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.25,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu não tenho um coração que possa tremer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o astro da música\Nestá passando mal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:48.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fala sério! Vocês não crescem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:54.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então nem todos estão aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:57.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim, o Chopper foi buscá-los.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.63,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá vêm eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:10.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu os trouxe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:23.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:31.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Que saudades!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês parecem bem mais fortes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora estamos todos juntos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:44.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:46.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:08.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, obrigado por tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Manda um abraço meu pra todo\Nmundo do Reino dos Pássaros!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:14.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! O Sanji está bem?!
Dialogue: 50,0:23:14.81,0:23:18.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,U-Uma linda mulher...
Dialogue: 50,0:23:18.01,0:23:20.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, fale comigo!
Dialogue: 50,0:23:18.91,0:23:20.52,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Duas lindas mulheres...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:20.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:23.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa não, Chopper!\NPare o sangramento!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:28.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,F-Franky, você...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:29.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:33.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está intrigado com algo-robô?
Dialogue: 50,0:23:34.30,0:23:37.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,- Robô?! Quero brincar!
Dialogue: 50,0:23:36.23,0:23:37.20,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:40.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vejo graça alguma nisso,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:42.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e parece que a Marinha já está aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não! Quando eles chegaram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:51.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há três navios da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:58.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vamos revidar?!\NEles vão nos pegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.57,0:24:01.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atirem! Atirem e afundem-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:05.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sureibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.57,0:24:07.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Arō!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:15.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.52,0:24:17.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-São...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:22.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As Piratas Kuja!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.89,0:24:26.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.93,0:24:30.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,colocou um navio da Marinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.93,0:24:34.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,no meu caminho?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:44.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o emblema das Kuja!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.64,0:24:45.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kuja?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.91,0:24:50.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São poderosas piratas amazonas lideradas\Npor uma imperatriz pirata e Shichibukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:52.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shichibukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:54.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela se chama Boa Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.25,0:24:57.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dizem que qualquer um que a vê\Nse apaixona por sua beleza
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:25:00.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e acaba transformado em pedra.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:02.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, que deslumbrante!\NEla é de outro mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.50,0:25:05.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A beleza dela não tem fim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.73,0:25:08.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rapaz! Mas é uma deusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.50,0:25:10.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma deusa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.17,0:25:13.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê? Deusa?! Deusa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.14,0:25:17.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deusa... Ah, deusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.05,0:25:20.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Virou pedra!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.18,0:25:23.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é o barco da Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:26.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saia do caminho, Boa Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.32,0:25:29.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está tentando interferir com\No cumprimento do nosso dever?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.06,0:25:31.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nada disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.99,0:25:35.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só não quero abrir caminho para vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.16,0:25:37.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ela está agindo feito uma criança!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.96,0:25:38.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Algum problema?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:44.14,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Vá, Luffy. Agora é a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.64,0:25:48.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela piscou na nossa direção...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.81,0:25:51.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela nos ajudou.\NVamos partir agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.31,0:25:52.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você conhece essa Shichibukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.28,0:25:57.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu fui parar na Ilha\Ndas Mulheres e fiquei amigo delas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.78,0:26:00.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A lendária ilha habitada só por mulheres?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.85,0:26:02.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sabia que existia mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.69,0:26:05.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Amigo da Imperatriz Pirata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.86,0:26:09.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, e você treinou mesmo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.90,0:26:11.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, estou pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.13,0:26:13.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é justo! Não é justo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.97,0:26:15.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.37,0:26:20.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossa, então aqueles são\Nos companheiros do Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.67,0:26:23.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há umas criaturas que nunca vi antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.81,0:26:26.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,- Um, dois, três, quatro...\N- Parece que estão se divertindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.18,0:26:30.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos preparar para partir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.32,0:26:32.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,- Sim!\N- Sim, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.85,0:26:34.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.22,0:26:39.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por curiosidade, vocês derrotaram\Ntodos os soldados da Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.39,0:26:43.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não... Quando alçamos vôo,\Nainda ouvíamos eles gritando.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.53,0:26:47.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então por que não continuaram\Nnos perseguindo até esta ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.51,0:26:57.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelotão 3 da Unidade de Reforço falando!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.64,0:26:58.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Copiam?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.11,0:27:02.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve? O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.02,0:27:04.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não conseguimos chegar ao Mangue #42!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.58,0:27:05.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.79,0:27:06.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.12,0:27:10.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há insetos gigantes impedindo nosso caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.52,0:27:11.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Insetos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.23,0:27:16.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que são essas coisas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.53,0:27:21.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:33.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não permitirei que atrapalhem\Na nova aventura do Usopp'm!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.65,0:27:39.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando homens se despedem,\Nnão derramam lágrimas'm!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.55,0:27:42.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte, Usopp'm!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.13,0:27:47.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Contanto que eles não venham, tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.59,0:27:49.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se eles estiverem encrencados,\Nsorte a nossa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.93,0:27:52.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos logo embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.37,0:27:54.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami, você comanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.83,0:27:55.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conte comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.57,0:27:58.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.71,0:28:02.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelotão 4 na linha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.51,0:28:05.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito. De repente, começou a chover
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.58,0:28:07.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e a pólvora molhou!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.15,0:28:09.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chuva? Onde?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.22,0:28:13.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O céu do Arquipélago Sabaody deveria\Nestar claro e ensolarado!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.96,0:28:23.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem trovões... Não queremos machucar os civis!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.23,0:28:26.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As bolhas aqui atrapalham bastante...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.37,0:28:29.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas não acredito que pegamos\Num vento tão perfeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.84,0:28:32.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele nos trouxe bem aonde precisávamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.07,0:28:36.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É porque a Nami é uma boa menina.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.48,0:28:45.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte! Sentiremos sua\Nfalta em Climatéria!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.50,0:29:03.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, está inflando!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:08.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Esta gelatina infla?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:15.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos dentro de uma bolha!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.72,0:29:16.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escutem bem, pessoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.45,0:29:21.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um navio revestido consegue reduzir qualquer tipo\Nde pressão.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.26,0:29:26.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Portanto, quando removermos a bolsa\Nflutuante presa à popa do navio,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.29,0:29:31.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a bolha vai anular o empuxo\Ne o Sunny revestido afundará.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:32.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É assim que funciona.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.00,0:29:34.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.47,0:29:35.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Complicado, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.74,0:29:37.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enfim, desfraldem as velas agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.94,0:29:38.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As velas?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.77,0:29:42.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um navio revestido é impulsionado\Npelas correntes marítimas, e não pelo vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.14,0:29:45.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei que fosse só submergir e navegar...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.51,0:29:49.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos antes que\Na Marinha apareça de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.72,0:29:54.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelotão 5 da Unidade Central\Ndo Mangue #42 falando!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.39,0:29:55.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Emergência!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.79,0:29:59.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos os soldados do\NPelotão 2 estão deprimidos...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.73,0:30:01.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como assim, deprimidos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.73,0:30:03.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero virar musgo...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.10,0:30:05.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não presto...\NQuero virar uma pulga d'água...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.07,0:30:08.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles dizem que o Chapéu de Palha
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:10.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,montou num pássaro\Ngigante e foi embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.70,0:30:13.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um pássaro? E o que vocês\Nestão fazendo agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.54,0:30:16.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos enfrentando inimigos\Nnão-identificados!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:20.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Reforços da Marinha logo na hora que estamos partindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.88,0:30:22.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.75,0:30:27.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O navio dos Chapéus de Palha está no perímetro!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.52,0:30:31.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera um pouco!\NUm pássaro gigante está nos seguindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.70,0:30:42.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.50,0:30:45.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Também estão vindo pela retaguarda!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.11,0:30:47.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:51.08,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Que tal, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.51,0:30:55.15,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Viu como fiquei mais forte?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.42,0:30:58.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.52,0:31:03.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Responda, Pelotão 5!\NO que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.39,0:31:05.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Nós estamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.63,0:31:09.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos encarando um\Nobstáculo inesperado...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.96,0:31:11.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não façam isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.33,0:31:18.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como podem nos recusar?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.30,0:31:20.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai ver, são todos tímidos...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.41,0:31:23.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não precisam ter vergonha!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.21,0:31:26.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos tomar chá juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.75,0:31:31.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,M-Meu coração... Meu coração não aguenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.42,0:31:37.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Que rostinho fofo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.62,0:31:39.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.16,0:31:44.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve? Responda, Pelotão 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.60,0:31:49.00,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji, a hora é essa!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:53.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! O que foi, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.91,0:31:57.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eu não sei... De repente, eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.04,0:32:00.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Senti como se estivessem\Nespremendo meu coração...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.15,0:32:01.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A bolsa flutuante foi removida!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.05,0:32:04.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo! E as velas?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.32,0:32:06.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Basta dar o sinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.85,0:32:08.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hora de ir, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.39,0:32:10.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim. Ao seu comando, Capitão.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.60,0:32:18.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.47,0:32:25.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.14,0:32:30.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho muita coisa para contar a vocês,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.08,0:32:35.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas obrigado por aceitarem minha\Ndecisão egoísta de dois anos atrás!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.58,0:32:37.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não foi a primeira vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.08,0:32:41.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pois é! Você só olha\Npro próprio umbigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.13,0:32:49.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Contra-Almirante, o navio\Npirata está submergindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.63,0:32:51.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.00,0:32:53.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.03,0:32:57.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fazem ideia de como\Neles são cruéis? Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.50,0:32:58.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Contra-Almirante!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.81,0:33:02.44,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Cuide-se, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.55,0:33:07.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desfraldar velas!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.55,0:33:08.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,- Sim!\N- Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.29,0:33:19.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Partir!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.53,0:33:21.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.17,0:33:32.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos para a Ilha dos Homens-Peixe!
